shotgun_proj_test

Source: R/shotgun_proj_test.R
shotgun_proj_test.Rd

a helper function to geographically test projections

Usage

shotgun_proj_test(
  path_to_model_g,
  out_path,
  proj_test_list = c("EPSG:2277", "ESRI:102739"),
  units = "Foot",
  in_epoch_override = as.integer(as.POSIXct(Sys.time())),
  out_epoch_override = as.integer(as.POSIXct(Sys.time())),
  vdat_trans = FALSE,
  quiet = FALSE,
  default_g = FALSE,
  try_both = TRUE
)
